#12816
trader~
the trader~
The trader of the forest is here before you.
~
He is definetely of the ranger class, a weather-worn man who lives in
this forest, having even set up a place where others can come to
to trade animal furs, skins, pelts, and food.  He has been toughened
by life in the outdoors for the majority of his life, and could
probably kill you without any second thought or trouble if you were
to provoke him.
~
1074790403 0 500 C
22 0 0 3d16+600 0d0+0
20 0
112 112 1
13 13 13 13 25 13 13
0 0 0 0 0
0 64 0 0 33 1 3
0 0 0 0 0 0 112 3
> fight_prog 100~
mpechoat $n The trader grabs you by the arm, flips you completely off your feet and onto your back.  Before you can do anything he has pulled out a large knife and proceeds to slit your throat.  Guess it wasn't too bright to attack a man of the wilderness, was it?
mpechoaround $n The trader grabs $n by $s arm, flips $m off the ground and onto $s back.  $n is too stunned to do anything as the trader kneels down with a knife in hand, and slits $n's throat.
mpslay $n
~
