The arch of Oaks~
As you step onto the hard packed pathway, you immediately notice two towering
oak trees rising above you.  The great trees bowed by their own massive weight
have bent towards eachother...their trunks interwined as one far above
the ground.  The sounds of birds call out from the majestice branches, as
shafts of sunlight penetrate the impressive foliage.
~
