#12843
The base of the Falls~
You find yourself standing at the base of a might waterfall which towers
to the north.  The roar of it fills your ears as small water sylphs dance
around the in the spray as it hits the rocks below.  To the east you 
notice a small path leading up the cliff to the top of the waterfall, and
the river that the falls feed continues torwards the south.
~
~
