#12844
Path away from the Falls~
As you step away from the falls that rage to the east you see a steep 
trail leading back to the woods above the falls.  A porcupine skuttles
into the underbrush to your right and the dirt of the path beneath your
feet brings up small clouds of dust.  The sounds of the forest call to
you once more from above.
~
~
