#12847
The river slows~
As you travel along the river you see that it is moving sluggishly here.
Perhaps that is due to the delta you notice to the south, that seems to
empty out into a lake.  To the north you hear the pounding roar of a 
mighty waterfall, but around you there is nothing to see but trees and
and tiny silver fish darting below the surface.
~
